*Postanem* ponosan na sebe. (I become proud of myself.)

Razmišljam da *postanem* profesionalni sportista. (I'm thinking to become a professional athlete.)

Ona *postade* žena njegovih snova. (She became the woman of his dreams.)

*Postao* sam svestan činjenice da je vreme za promene. (I became aware of the fact that it was time for changes.)

Svi su se zapitali kako se to dogodilo i zašto se on *postao* takav. (Everyone wondered how it happened and why he became like that.)